      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KINSTONS ANGEL (6) is heading the right way. Out of the placings two back then scored by 6 lengths last start at this track over 400m (24.13). Jumps a level but on latest effort worth sticking with her. JEOPARDY PANTHER (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Bombay Flash (24.44) in an A4. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in this for a long way. STORMTROOPER (5) has good credentials for this, winning an A4 two back before finishing runner-up at his latest appearance in an A4 at this track over 400m (24.51). This easier so don't rule him out. PAVILION HOGGIE (3) is worth including after a top-three finish from the same draw most recently.",
